high_descs: Turn around to walk to the bathtub.
Pick up the sponge from the bathtub.
Turn around to walk towards the metal shelf.
Put the sponge on the metal shelf next to the black rag.
Make a right to walk across the room to the toilet.
Pick up the sponge from the lid of the toilet tank.
Turn around to make a left to walk across the room to the metal shelf.
Put the other sponge on the metal shelf next to the black rag.
anns.task_desc: Put two sponges on the metal shelf.

high_descs: Turn right and walk over to the sink, then turn right and walk up to the tub.
Pick up the sponge out of the tub.
Turn right and walk over to the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the metal shelving unit in the corner of the room.
Put the sponge on the top shelf of the metal shelving unit.
Turn right and walk over to the white shelves on the wall, then turn right and walk up to the toilet.
Pick up the sponge off of the toilet tank.
Walk back over to the metal shelving unit in the corner of the room behind you.
Put the sponge on the top shelf of the metal shelving unit.
anns.task_desc: Move two sponges to a metal shelving unit.
